title: The Frozen Dead (1966) 95 min.DVDRip Dana Andrews Kathleen Breck
description:
The Frozen Dead:   

Twisted tale of Nazi experiments in suspended animation. Frozen remains of Nazi war
criminals are carefully preserved until they can be successfully revived. This process may require a test subject or two who doesn't mind having their head decapitated and the top of their skull removed.....Any volunteers?

Stars: Dana Andrews, Anna Palk, Philip Gilbert, .....Kathleen Breck
